{"tid":2097174,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[嘔心藍店] 南豐紗廠泰國餐廳極度嘔心！","createTime":"2020-07-06T15:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T04:05:47.000Z","uid":356276,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51f09a8279976145f4bb7224e19b103d92f02ca3","tid":2097174,"uid":356276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"南豐紗廠一樓最尾間泰國餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺度做咗一排 頂唔順走咗 <br />\n廚房入面勁污糟 最頂唔順係啲廚房啊姐<br />\n自己飲到一半嘅嘢飲 竟然refill返啲落去就出俾客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾錯嘢飲 有客return返嚟 但飲過一兩啖 個啊姐都照出返嗰杯俾其他客 真心不解嗰小小嘢飲慳乜鳩 <br />\n食個飯搞到中肺炎就無謂 呢間黑店真係要避 <br />\n大佬依家武漢肺炎咁嚴重都夠膽死咁做<br />\n無人想食你口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />長期見佢咁做<br />\n見好多人去紗廠打卡會食埋嘢 真係要小心咪中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得提醒埋屋企人 尤其係鐘意帶狗狗去紗廠玩嘅巴絲利申:講大話死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e780472da29cb919dae642c0f6817788e8f4603","tid":2097174,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"有無諗過間間餐廳都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ebae7ec6b3f4f18ba6fff7b67d1c171d70aa4c","tid":2097174,"uid":24356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"間野長期無客"},{"pid":"620a0794dfdbf1829da72473884447a927a943e5","tid":2097174,"uid":356276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16ebae7ec6b3f4f18ba6fff7b67d1c171d70aa4c","tid":2097174,"uid":24356,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"間野長期無客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"都唔係 工廠區返工既巴絲打平日會過嚟幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df037408783c5